	<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 31.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">为进一步贯彻落实勤俭办事精神，大力推进高效型、节约型、廉洁型机关建设，经委党政联席会议研究决定，就本委推进建设</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312"> </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">节约型机关制定如下工作制度，望各科室认真遵照执行。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 31.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">一、规范公务接待</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 31.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">．本着</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">热情、周到、节俭</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">的原则，做好公务接待。严格用餐标准，控制陪餐人数，提倡</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">光盘</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">行动。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 31.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>2</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">．在昆山区域以外的公务活动，贯彻节俭原则，包括会议费、招待费等均使用个人公务卡结算（严禁使用现金支付）。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 31.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>3</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">．在昆山的公务接待，住宿、用餐安排在固定的公务接待点（委公务接待点：一醉皇冠酒店、君豪酒店、玉峰大厦、华东国际商务酒店、银峰老鹅馆开发区店、昆山宾馆、奥灶馆），严格按照接待标准执行。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>4</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">．所有公务接待，具体承办科室须到办公室领取重大活动审批表，先提出申请，确定接待人数、接待标准、接待对象，限定陪同人员，经办公室主任、分管领导和主要领导签字后方可接待。审批表填完后交办公室，由办公室根据市政府定点接待地点统一安排，不得超标准接待。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>5</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">．委机关工作人员到企业调研时，原则上不在企业用餐，确须用餐的严格执行工作餐。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 31.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">二、精简工作会议</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">．严格执行会议活动报批制度，减少大型会议的数量，简化会议程序，缩短会议时间。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>2</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">．会议要讲究实效，控制出席人数，如需租用会议室时要适中，不租用高档酒店会议室，不宴请与会人员、不发纪念品、不摆放花草、不讲排场、不摆阔气，严禁浪费。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 31.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>3</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">．能够在网上发布的文件尽量不召开会议，不印发材料，能在一个会议上讨论的议题不再分开开会。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 31.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">三、节约用电</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 31.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">．合理设置空调温度，办公室、会议室等办公区域夏季温度设置不低于</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>26</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">摄氏度；冬季空调温度设置不高于</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>20</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">摄氏度，做到无人时不开空调，开空调时不开门窗。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 31.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>2</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">．办公室、会议室、走廊、通道等场所全部使用节能灯具，尽量采用自然光照明，做到人去灯熄，杜绝长明灯。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 31.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>3</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">．计算机、打印机、复印机、电视机等电器设备，在不使用时要及时关机，减少待机耗电。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 31.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>4</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">．办公室禁止使用电炉、电水壶、电取暖器、热得快等大功率用电器（具）。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 31.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>5</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">．加强对水电管道、照明线路、照明用灯的检修，严防漏、跑、冒、耗现象发生。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 31.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">四、节约用水</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 31.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">．机关工作人员要采取有效措施，节约每一滴水，树立勤俭节约的传统美德。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 31.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>2</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">．积极推广使用节水器具，用水后要及时关好水阀，杜绝跑冒滴漏，使用自来水龙头应轻开轻关，以免损坏。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 31.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>3</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">．加强供水管线的巡查，发现有管道泄漏的情况及时处理，防止水资源的无谓浪费。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 31.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">五、节约公务用车燃油</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 31.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">．加强公车燃油管理，实行定点加油制度，努力降低燃油消耗。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 31.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>2</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">．建立以单车为单位油耗台帐，并按月公布。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 31.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>3</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">．合理安排车辆出行路线和用车人员搭配，减少车辆空驶里程，提高公务用车的使用效率；提倡在集体公务活动集中乘车；非紧急公务外出尽量乘座公共交通，原则上科室人员外出不安排车辆；严禁公车私用。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 31.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">六、节约办公用品</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 31.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">．严格办公用品配置标准，根据市政府采购办的要求，计算机、打印机最低使用年限为</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>6</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年，如要更换需专业技术人员鉴定后，科室提出申请，由分管领导以及主要领导签字后方可采购。政府采购原则上以国产品牌为主，以耗能低为原则。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US> <o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 31.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>2</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">．推行电子政务，尽量在电子媒介上处理文稿，使用网络传递资料，除保密要求规定外的实行公文报送网上传输，积极推行无纸化办公。强化办公耗材的管理，办公耗材由办公室统一采购（严禁使用现金支付）。本着节俭原则，提倡双面用纸、降低纸张消耗，减少重复打印、复印次数，注重稿纸、复印纸的再利用，打印机、复印机的墨粉用完后，能重新灌装的要重复利用。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 31.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>3</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">．办公电话尽可能做到语言精炼准确，减少通话时间。尽量使用虚拟网小号和内线，杜绝电话聊天、开设电话增值服务等业务。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 31.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>4</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">．循环使用办公用品，提倡使用钢笔书写，减少一次性签字笔的使用。饮水提倡使用茶杯，尽量减少一次性纸杯和瓶装饮用水。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
